    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational, there are visible signs of wear including some minor fluid seepage and typical high-mileage engine noise. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and floor mats. All safety features are intact, making this a solid choice for those who value utility and mechanical function over cosmetic perfection.",
